                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                    </span>
                    <h3
                        class="mb-1 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
                    >
                        Software Developer (Part-time) - OrangeKloud, Inc
                    </h3>
                    <time
                        class="block mb-2 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-500"
